.SH NAME
.PP
jx\-gitops\-helm\-release \- Performs a release of all the charts in the charts folder


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBjx\-gitops helm release\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Generate the kubernetes resources from a helm chart


